 886:MyHardWare/eMPL/inv_mpu.c ****   /* For LP accel, we automatically configure the hardware to produce latched
 887:MyHardWare/eMPL/inv_mpu.c ****    * interrupts. In LP accel mode, the hardware cycles into sleep mode before
 888:MyHardWare/eMPL/inv_mpu.c ****    * it gets a chance to deassert the interrupt pin; therefore, we shift this
 889:MyHardWare/eMPL/inv_mpu.c ****    * responsibility over to the MCU.
 890:MyHardWare/eMPL/inv_mpu.c ****    *
 891:MyHardWare/eMPL/inv_mpu.c ****    * Any register read will clear the interrupt.
 892:MyHardWare/eMPL/inv_mpu.c ****    */
